        h3.
          What are common #[br]triggers of binge eating?
        p.
          As noted in #[em DSM-5]#[sup ®], negative affect most commonly precedes a bingeing episode.#[sup 1] 

        p.
          Other triggers include#[sup 1]:
        
        ul.bullet
          li
            | Interpersonal stressors
          li
            | Restrictions on diet
          li
            | Feeling badly about body weight, body shape, and food
          li
            | Feeling bored
        
